Rodney H. HOLMES, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-1718 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. OCTOBER 01, 2018 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and SALTER and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Upon the Court's own motion, it is ordered that the above styled appeal is hereby dismissed. See Holmes v. State , 245 So. 3d 1008 (Fla. 3d DCA 2018).
